ms ease, transform 200ms ease;min-height:120px\" class=\"hover:bg-[var(--color-surface)] hover:-translate-y-0.5\" href=\"/categories/understanding-your-dog\"><span style=\"font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:18px;color:var(--color-ink);line-height:1.2\">Understanding Your Dog</span><span style=\"color:var(--color-muted);font-size:13px;line-height:1.4\">Reading the signals, the science of doggy emotions, and what your friend is really telling you.</span></a><a style=\"background:var(--color-surface-cream);border-radius:16px;padding:20px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:8px;border:1px solid var(--color-hairline-soft);transition:background 200ms ease, transform 200ms ease;min-height:120px\" class=\"hover:bg-[var(--color-surface)] hover:-translate-y-0.5\" href=\"/categories/getting-a-dog\"><span style=\"font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:18px;color:var(--color-ink);line-height:1.2\">Getting a Dog</span><span style=\"color:var(--color-muted);font-size:13px;line-height:1.4\">From first thoughts to first walk home</span></a><a style=\"background:var(--color-surface-cream);border-radius:16px;padding:20px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:8px;border:1px solid var(--color-hairline-soft);transition:background 200ms ease, transform 200ms ease;min-height:120px\" class=\"hover:bg-[var(--color-surface)] hover:-translate-y-0.5\" href=\"/categories/health-wellbeing\"><span style=\"font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:18px;color:var(--color-ink);line-height:1.2\">Health &amp; Wellbeing</span><span style=\"color:var(--color-muted);font-size:13px;line-height:1.4\">Vet-reviewed guides on everyday care, warning signs, and life-stage health.</span></a><a style=\"background:var(--color-surface-cream);border-radius:16px;padding:20px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:8px;border:1px solid var(--color-hairline-soft);transition:background 200ms ease, transform 200ms ease;min-height:120px\" class=\"hover:bg-[var(--color-surface)] hover:-translate-y-0.5\" href=\"/categories/life-with-your-dog\"><span style=\"font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:18px;color:var(--color-ink);line-height:1.2\">Life With Your Dog</span><span style=\"color:var(--color-muted);font-size:13px;line-height:1.4\">Travel, holidays, families, and the everyday joys of dog life.</span></a><a style=\"background:var(--color-surface-cream);border-radius:16px;padding:20px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:8px;border:1px solid var(--color-hairline-soft);transition:background 200ms ease, transform 200ms ease;min-height:120px\" class=\"hover:bg-[var(--color-surface)] hover:-translate-y-0.5\" href=\"/categories/puppy-care\"><span style=\"font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:18px;color:var(--color-ink);line-height:1.2\">Puppy Care</span><span style=\"color:var(--color-muted);font-size:13px;line-height:1.4\">The first weeks and months</span></a></div></div></section><section style=\"background:var(--color-surface-soft)\"><div class=\"mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-10 py-16 lg:py-24 grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-10 lg:gap-16 items-center\" style=\"max-width:1444px\"><div class=\"relative\" style=\"border-radius:24px;overflow:hidden;aspect-ratio:5 / 4;box-shadow:0 8px 28px rgba(0,0,0,0.12)\"><img alt=\"Blue-Eyed Dog Health Problems: Causes, Symptoms &amp;amp; Treatment\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;object-fit:cover;color:transparent\" src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1601758228041-f3b2795255f1?auto=format&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=1200&amp;q=80\"/></div><div><span style=\"display:inline-block;background:var(--color-surface);color:var(--color-ink);padding:4px 14px;border-radius:9999px;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:1.2px;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:16px\">Featured story</span><h2 style=\"font-family:var(--font-display);margin-bottom:16px\">Blue-Eyed Dog Health Problems: Causes, Symptoms &amp;amp; Treatment</h2><p style=\"font-size:18px;color:var(--color-body);margin-bottom:24px;line-height:1.6\">Discover common health problems in blue-eyed dogs, including symptoms, causes, and treatment options. Learn how to protect your pup&#x27;s vision and hearing.</p><a class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center\" style=\"background:transparent;color:var(--color-ink);border-radius:32px;padding:0 24px;height:48px;font-size:16px;font-weight:600;border:2px solid var(--color-ink)\" href=\"/blog/blue-eyed-dog-health-problems-treatment\">Read the full story</a></div></div></section><section class=\"grid lg:grid-cols-2\" style=\"background:var(--color-primary)\"><div class=\"px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-10 py-16 lg:py-20 flex items-center\" style=\"background:var(--color-primary)\"><div style=\"max-width:540px;margin-left:auto\"><h2 style=\"font-family:var(--font-display);color:var(--color-on-primary);margin-bottom:20px\">Will you help dogs live their best life?</h2><p style=\"font-size:18px;color:var(--color-on-primary);font-weight:500;line-height:1.6;margin-bottom:28px\">Our authors — vets, trainers, behaviour specialists — write to help dogs and their humans understand each other a little more every week. Read their work, share what helps you, tell a friend.</p><a class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center\" style=\"background:var(--color-ink);color:var(--color-primary);border-radius:32px;padding:0 28px;height:56px;font-size:16px;font-weight:600;border:2px solid var(--color-ink)\" href=\"/authors\">Meet our authors</a></div></div><div style=\"background:var(--color-canvas);position:relative;min-height:320px\"><img alt=\"A small terrier resting on a cushion\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;object-fit:cover;color:transparent\" src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1576201836106-db1758fd1c97?auto=format&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=1200&amp;q=80\"/></div></section><section style=\"background:var(--color-canvas)\"><div cla